high_descs: Turn around and exit the room on the left to walk down the passage and turn right to reach the bed.
Pick up the glass bowl from the bed.
Turn around to reach the dresser.
Put the bowl on the dresser.
Turn around to walk past the bed and exit the room on the right and turn left to walk down the passage and turn left to reach the shelf under the tvstand.
Pick up the bowl from the shelf.
Turn left to reach the passage and turn right to reach the end and turn right to reach the dresser on the left.
Put the bowl on the right of the other bowl on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Put the two bowls on the dresser.

high_descs: Turn around, go outside the room through the upper left exit, turn right and head straight to the end of the hallway with a picture on the wall, where you enter a room on the right and walk to the longer side of the bed.
Pick up the bowl from the bed.
Turn around and walk to the dresser on the left.
Place the bowl on the top of the dresser.
Go to the same entrance you used to enter the room, go left and turn to a shelf stand that is under a tvstand.
Pick up the bowl from the stand.
Go back to the same dresser you came from.
Put the bowl on the top of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Place two bowls on the top of dresser furniture.

high_descs: Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the bed.
Pick up bowl from the bed.
Head towards the door, then hang a left and go to the dresser.
Place bowl on the dresser.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the tv stand on your right.
Pick up bowl from the bed.
Head towards the door, then hang a left and go to the dresser.
Place bowl on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Collecting bowl from different places and arranging them on a dresser.
